      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start, but it's a bit general. for a competitive debate, my students need more depth. could you expand on the 'national sovereignty' and 'rule of law' points? like, what are the specific philosophical or legal arguments used to justify why a state has the absolute right to control its borders above all else? i need them to be able to argue this from a high level, not just a policy level.",
